://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F6bEAZWqAHtNXV5NKdSFHSv0fVwI%3D%2F950x640%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FQBK4MVNYZRAPRCCHNORJW7SZZE.jpg&h=ec910483&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■獲本年度評論學會最佳電影的《理大圍城》，於一片爭議聲中上映。"}]}